Third-party notices:

- `src/zipenhancer_repro/vendor/zipenhancer_community/` contains the minimum
  community ModelScope ZipEnhancer implementation needed for strict-load
  compatibility with official weights. Original author metadata is preserved
  in the vendored source files.
- `src/zipenhancer_repro/optim/_icefall_optim.py` adapts ScaledAdam/Eden
  optimizer code from icefall.
- `src/zipenhancer_repro/losses/mpsenet_loss.py` adapts MP-SENet-style
  multi-resolution losses and PESQ-GAN discriminator logic for reproduction.

Official model weights are not redistributed. Download them separately and
place them under a local ignored directory such as `checkpoints/official/`.
